{"tid":1597634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"料林鄭有「被困」心理準備   湯家驊滿意效果","createTime":"2019-09-27T04:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T07:19:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"4634b8af9c2d62950723c591bf222327a9ff7b61","tid":1597634,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:42:34.000Z","msg":"政府昨晚在灣仔伊利沙伯體育館舉行首場「社區對話」，行政會議成員湯家驊今日表示，對「對話會」的效果感到相當滿意，也對無出現暴力事件而鬆一口氣，希望政府很快會再舉行「社區對話」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊早上在一電台節目中表示，雖然滿意昨日的「對話會」，但不能期望一次對話便能解決深層次矛盾，但這是好的開始，能塑造一個平和理性的場合讓市民抒發怨憤和表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n對於「對話會」完場時有在場人士喊口號，湯家驊認為無可厚非；而特首林鄭月娥完場後因場外有反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威者聚集而被困4小時，他也相信特首已有心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190927/_2019092710505586439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190927%2F_2019092710505586439.jpg&h=a62eb5ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1600645/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E6%9C%83-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E6%BB%BF%E6%84%8F%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C-%E6%96%99%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%89-%E8%A2%AB%E5%9B%B0-%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a7eb3008c6cad7047c848c0b99e3a613500a66b5","tid":1597634,"uid":301523,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"敵人滿意..點算?"},{"pid":"95b805ffdcaec0cdf7d56acdf82f5a056a7545b9","tid":1597634,"uid":122059,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"敵人讚好的事情 我們堅決反對"},{"pid":"8c5d04bfe2281d85a88b27ecbad7c9dfaff99eea","tid":1597634,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7eb3008c6cad7047c848c0b99e3a613500a66b5","tid":1597634,"uid":301523,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"敵人滿意..點算?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\